    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Linum is a puzzle game that will test your logical thinking skills. 50+ handcrafted levels designed to teach, test and challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made by one person, it's challenging and for all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles aimed at pushing the limits rather than &quot;more of the same&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original artwork and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No microtransaction/DLC/subscription, DRM-free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable with mouse, keyboard, controller or any combination of these.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of the game is to create a matching image of the objective while consuming all the resources available. The resources are either creator or modifiers.</p>",
